<article class="main-article" data-aid="21793175">
<header>
<h1>Khi giám thị 'gà bài' cho thí sinh</h1>
<p class="meta ">
<a class="source" href="/giaoduc.net.vn-bao-giao-duc-viet-nam-giao-duc-vn/p/231.epi">Giáo Dục VN</a>
<time datetime="2017-03-18T07:42:00+07:00">18/03/2017 07:42 GMT+7</time>
<a id="main_hlRelevanceCount" href="/gian-lan-thi-hsg-o-nghe-an/t/2088486.epi">62 liên quan</a>
</p>
</header>
